>\n噏下個概念就攞晒credit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲扮埋大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n笑唔笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7a491f74bde5c7a8c6c6db011f17a900f1fd131","tid":370424,"uid":46151,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T22:03:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果無父幹無家底 <br />\n佢人生分分鐘只係做企七仔或者m記派餐咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n懶高深真係想打柒佢<br />\n有撚才華咩<br />\n啲嘢都唔係佢寫既</blockquote><br />\n雖然佢冇落手寫份詞 但佢有份諗個概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且呢啲唔太mk同唔太k歌嘅歌 通常都冇乜市場<br />\n唱片公司都唔會肯俾你出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n誇張的講 冇佢冇呢啲咁嘅歌</blockquote><br />\n唔係同你講詞<br />\n作曲編曲都唔係落佢名<br />\n噏下個概念就攞晒credit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲扮埋大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n笑唔笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n麥浚龍是幸運的。得父蔭，起跑線上贏到開巷？我指的不是這個。「有錢，都要你有品味嘅。」此乃網民對他的點評，喂，中肯喎！「初出道的Juno都叫有品味？」問世間誰沒核突過呢？年少無知，人皆歷之。鏟青同時鏟走MK味，他從高唱無甚營養的K歌到找到自己的風格，走偏鋒、玩意境、闖難度，概念大碟接連推出，曲詞編到MV，每樣都令人嘩嘩聲。「唓，曲又唔係佢作，詞又唔係佢寫，歌藝又唔係特別好。」你啱！他有的不是音樂才華，是前瞻與膽量，還有煲盡B片、cult片、恐怖片，再蒸餾出自己的怪雞美學。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/special/art/20150730/19236338\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fspecial%2Fart%2F20150730%2F19236338&d=HTQbVdZbBIArdKwCPeMvPZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=8e4d3284\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fspecial%2Fart%2F20150730%2F19236338&h=de84f8f5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/special/art/20150730/19236338</a><br />\nbtw 做導演算唔算有才華<br />\n定係佢唔係編劇所以都係冇才華"},{"pid":"09414a8f7d6fb8c40f96f7681683a8f674133cf4","tid":3704